<section id="HE8A2148622E745A1A49C9FF183B02C43" section-type="section-one"><enum>1.</enum><header>National pollutant discharge elimination system (NPDES) terms</header> 
<subsection id="H391C70C61CBE4917A74D604B3CDC781B"><enum>(a)</enum><header>In general</header><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Section 402(b)(1)(B) of the Federal Water Pollution Control Act (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/33/1342">33 U.S.C. 1342(b)(1)(B)</external-xref>) is amended to read as follows:</text> <quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="HF8523AB3B6C44E0F926129924B68D278" style="OLC"> <subparagraph id="H7FF0E4F066EF45E997D63A5EFE97DB0D" indent="up1"><enum>(B)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">are for fixed terms—</text> 
<clause id="H9966112D3A8B4F59AF1022EA8A1D80A0"><enum>(i)</enum><text>not exceeding 10 years, for a permit issued to a State or municipality; and</text></clause> <clause id="H353914D10C8544709FE5176A0EB6876C"><enum>(ii)</enum><text>not exceeding 5 years, for a permit issued to any person not described in clause (i); and</text></clause></subparagraph><after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block></quoted-block></subsection> 
<subsection id="HE986762C486B44AFB7FCD737C7764FFC" commented="no"><enum>(b)</enum><header>Technical corrections</header><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Section 402(<italic>l</italic>)(3) of the Federal Water Pollution Control Act (33 U.S.C. 1342(<italic>l</italic>)(3)) is amended—</text> <paragraph id="HB4ECF23BFFCD43CA8D0AFD29F9B8964D" commented="no"><enum>(1)</enum><text>in subparagraph (B)—</text> 
<subparagraph id="H60B30722919845D0B205082BE30075B0" commented="no"><enum>(A)</enum><text>by striking <quote>section 402</quote> and inserting <quote>this section</quote>; and</text></subparagraph> <subparagraph id="H4F0487FC6BA3407F954C738A411BDD05" commented="no"><enum>(B)</enum><text>by striking <quote>federal</quote> and inserting <quote>Federal</quote>; and </text></subparagraph></paragraph> 
<paragraph id="HF46CE7EED1964D35889585CD1EFE13CB" commented="no"><enum>(2)</enum><text>in subparagraph (C)—</text> <subparagraph id="HD0D84346C7A242CF8720936C14BE89A3" commented="no"><enum>(A)</enum><text>by striking <quote>Section</quote> and inserting <quote>section</quote>;</text></subparagraph> 
<subparagraph id="H3336AF33D8A54452AA19CE0F959539A9" commented="no"><enum>(B)</enum><text>by striking <quote>402(p)(6)</quote> and inserting <quote>subsection (p)(6)</quote>;</text></subparagraph> <subparagraph id="H302BCC3DFD3E48228DB451327FCECF5A" commented="no"><enum>(C)</enum><text>by striking <quote>402(l)(3)(A),</quote> and inserting <quote>subparagraph (A),</quote>; and</text></subparagraph> 
<subparagraph id="H072B2764C2FA4111ADEE228BE13553AC" commented="no"><enum>(D)</enum><text>by striking <quote>402(l)(3)(A).</quote> and inserting <quote>such subparagraph.</quote>.</text></subparagraph></paragraph> </subsection></section> </legis-body></bill> 

